251
00:18:41,997 --> 00:18:43,290
She died.

252
00:18:45,375 --> 00:18:46,585
I'm sorry.

253
00:18:46,668 --> 00:18:50,297
Oh, don't be.
She believed in heaven, so she's covered.

254
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:52,924
You know, afterlife-wise?

255
00:19:01,725 --> 00:19:04,853
- What's this?
- She left it for you.

256
00:19:05,061 --> 00:19:08,398
I think she hoped it would help me,

257
00:19:08,482 --> 00:19:10,901
you know, get a job here.

258
00:19:10,984 --> 00:19:13,653
But of course.
Gusteau wouldn't hesitate.

259
00:19:13,737 --> 00:19:14,821
Any son of Renata's is more than...

260
00:19:14,905 --> 00:19:18,575
Yes, well, we could file this and
if something suitable opens up...

261
00:19:18,658 --> 00:19:19,743
We have already hired him.

262
00:19:19,826 --> 00:19:23,580
What? How dare you
hire someone without my...

263
00:19:23,663 --> 00:19:25,415
We needed a garbage boy.

264
00:19:26,082 --> 00:19:28,543
Oh, garbage. Well...

265
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:30,420
I'm glad it worked out.

266
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:41,598
I can't believe it.

267
00:19:41,848 --> 00:19:45,060
A real gourmet kitchen,
and I get to watch.

268
00:19:45,268 --> 00:19:48,396
You've read my book.
Let us see how much you know, huh?

269
00:19:48,563 --> 00:19:50,148
Which one is the chef?

270
00:19:52,567 --> 00:19:54,945
- Oh, that guy.
- Very good.

271
00:19:55,111 --> 00:19:56,655
Who is next in command?

272
00:19:56,738 --> 00:19:59,574
The sous chef. There.

273
00:19:59,866 --> 00:20:03,787
The sous is responsible for the kitchen
when the chef's not around.

274
00:20:04,037 --> 00:20:07,415
Saucier, in charge of sauces.
Very important.

275
00:20:07,582 --> 00:20:11,711
Chef de partie, demi chef de partie,
both important.

276
00:20:11,795 --> 00:20:14,631
Commis, commis, they're cooks.
Very important.

277
00:20:14,798 --> 00:20:17,926
You are a clever rat.
Now, who is that?

278
00:20:18,593 --> 00:20:20,720
Oh, him? He's nobody.

279
00:20:20,804 --> 00:20:22,889
Not nobody.
He is part of the kitchen.

280
00:20:22,973 --> 00:20:24,891
No, he's a <i>plongeuror</i> something.

281
00:20:24,975 --> 00:20:27,477
