He doesn't cook.

282
00:20:27,561 --> 00:20:30,814
- But he could.
- Uh, no.

283
00:20:30,897 --> 00:20:33,149
How do you know?
What do I always say?

284
00:20:33,233 --> 00:20:34,901
Anyone can cook.

285
00:20:34,985 --> 00:20:38,905
Well, yeah, anyone can.
That doesn't mean that anyone should.

286
00:20:38,989 --> 00:20:42,617
