One fillet mignon, three lamb, two duck.

297
00:22:36,106 --> 00:22:38,733
Fire those soufflés for table six, <i>ja</i>.

298
00:22:38,900 --> 00:22:40,860
- Five minutes, chef.
- Oh, God.

299
00:22:46,199 --> 00:22:48,618
Tonight, I'd like
to present the foie gras.

300
00:22:48,702 --> 00:22:50,453
It has a wonderful finish.

301
00:23:09,639 --> 00:23:12,058
