303
00:23:54,976 --> 00:23:56,895
Remy! What are you waiting for?

304
00:23:56,978 --> 00:23:58,813
Is this going to become
a regular thing with you?

305
00:23:58,897 --> 00:24:01,608
You know how to fix it.
This is your chance.

306
00:24:56,412 --> 00:25:00,917
The soup! Where is the soup?
Out of my way.

307
00:25:01,417 --> 00:25:03,586
Move it, garbage boy!

308
00:25:04,254 --> 00:25:06,881
You are cooking?

309
00:25:07,048 --> 00:25:10,510
How dare you cook in my kitchen?

310
00:25:10,593 --> 00:25:12,679
Where do you get the gall

311
00:25:12,762 --> 00:25:16,391
to even attempt something
so monumentally idiotic?

312
00:25:16,474 --> 00:25:18,518
