- It was not a customer. It was a critic.

326
00:26:30,882 --> 00:26:33,092
- Ego?
- Solene LeClaire.

327
00:26:33,176 --> 00:26:37,263
- LeClaire? What did she say?
- She likes the soup.

328
00:26:37,388 --> 00:26:39,057
- Wait.
- What do you mean, "Wait"?

329
00:26:39,140 --> 00:26:40,767
You're the reason I'm in this mess.

330
00:26:40,850 --> 00:26:42,268
Someone is asking about your soup.

331
00:26:52,362 --> 00:26:54,989
What are you playing at?

332
00:26:57,367 --> 00:26:58,618
Am I still fired?

333
00:26:58,701 --> 00:27:00,870
- You can't fire him.
- What?

334
00:27:00,954 --> 00:27:04,290
LeClaire likes it, yeah?
She made a point of telling you so.

335
00:27:04,374 --> 00:27:05,667
