or very unlucky.

353
00:28:03,516 --> 00:28:08,938
You will make the soup again,
and this time, I'll be paying attention.

354
00:28:09,147 --> 00:28:11,941
Very close attention.

355
00:28:12,233 --> 00:28:16,696
They think you might be a cook.
But you know what I think, Linguini?

356
00:28:16,904 --> 00:28:20,950
I think you are a sneaky,
overreaching little...

357
00:28:21,534 --> 00:28:22,785
Rat!

358
00:28:25,204 --> 00:28:26,748
