a rat in our kitchen?

365
00:28:40,261 --> 00:28:41,888
They'd close us down.

366
00:28:41,971 --> 00:28:44,390
Our reputation is hanging
by a thread as it is.

367
00:28:44,474 --> 00:28:48,644
Take it away from here. Far away.
Kill it. Dispose of it. Go!

368
00:29:25,306 --> 00:29:29,143
Don't look at me like that!
You aren't the only one who's trapped.

369
00:29:29,227 --> 00:29:31,395
They expect me to cook it again!

370
00:29:31,604 --> 00:29:34,398
I mean, I'm not ambitious.
I wasn't trying to cook.

371
00:29:34,482 --> 00:29:36,609
I was just trying to stay
out of trouble.

372
00:29:36,692 --> 00:29:39,779
You're the one who was
getting fancy with the spices!

373
00:29:39,862 --> 00:29:44,784
What did you throw in there? Oregano?
No? What? Rosemary?

374
00:29:45,034 --> 00:29:47,537
That's a spice, isn't it? Rosemary?

375
00:29:48,037 --> 00:29:50,540
You didn't throw rosemary in there?

376
00:29:50,832 --> 00:29:54,961
Then what was all the flipping
and all the throwing the...

