380
00:30:09,392 --> 00:30:11,561
Have you been nodding?

381
00:30:12,979 --> 00:30:14,772
You understand me?

382
00:30:15,273 --> 00:30:16,983
So I'm not crazy!

383
00:30:18,151 --> 00:30:20,236
Wait a second, wait a second.

384
00:30:21,279 --> 00:30:24,031
