You're a rat, for Pete's sake.

388
00:30:35,042 --> 00:30:37,461
Whatever you did, they liked it.

389
00:30:38,045 --> 00:30:40,631
Yeah. This could work.

390
00:30:41,424 --> 00:30:43,509
Hey, they liked the soup!

391
00:30:46,179 --> 00:30:51,267
They liked the soup.
Do you think you could do it again?

392
00:30:54,854 --> 00:30:57,315
Okay, I'm going to let you out now.

393
00:30:58,107 --> 00:31:01,277
But we're together on this. Right?

394
00:31:02,945 --> 00:31:04,488
Okay.

395
00:32:14,725 --> 00:32:16,686
So this is it.

396
00:32:17,144 --> 00:32:21,148
I mean, it's not much,
but it's, you know...

397
00:32:23,192 --> 00:32:24,568
Not much.

398
00:32:27,029 --> 00:32:28,281
It could be worse.

399
00:32:28,364 --> 00:32:30,783
There's heat and light
and a couch with a TV.

400
00:32:30,866 --> 00:32:33,369
So, you know, what's mine is yours.

401
00:32:34,370 --> 00:32:35,788
<i>Are you...</i>

402
00:32:35,871 --> 00:32:38,165
<i>Is this a dream?</i>

403
00:32:38,249 --> 00:32:40,584
<i>The best kind of dream.</i>

404
00:32:40,918 --> 00:32:43,254
<i>One we can share.</i>

405
00:32:43,337 --> 00:32:44,964
<i>But why here?</i>

406
00:32:45,464 --> 00:32:47,049
<i>Why now?</i>

407
00:32:47,925 --> 00:32:49,719
<i>Why not here?</i>

408
00:32:49,927 --> 00:32:51,721
<i>Why not now?</i>

409
00:32:52,471 --> 00:32:56,559
<i>What better place to dream
than in Paris?</i>

