00:33:13,367 --> 00:33:14,577
Oh, no.

412
00:33:16,412 --> 00:33:17,872
Idiot! I knew this would happen!

413
00:33:17,955 --> 00:33:20,791
I let a rat into my place and
tell him what's mine is his!

414
00:33:20,875 --> 00:33:22,001
Eggs, gone!

415
00:33:22,084 --> 00:33:25,504
Stupid! He's stolen food and hit the road!
What did I expect?

416
00:33:25,588 --> 00:33:28,132
That's what I get for trusting a...

417
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,595
