if we do this anymore.

443
00:36:16,258 --> 00:36:18,677
We've got to figure out
something else.

444
00:36:18,761 --> 00:36:21,013
Something that doesn't involve
any biting, or nipping,

445
00:36:21,096 --> 00:36:23,849
