472
00:38:38,734 --> 00:38:40,486
Wait. I'm sorry.

473
00:38:45,115 --> 00:38:46,241
Okay.

474
00:38:56,251 --> 00:38:57,252
Okay.

475
00:40:04,236 --> 00:40:05,654
All right.

476
00:40:32,556 --> 00:40:33,849
That should do it.

477
00:40:37,603 --> 00:40:42,649
